Package: fastlowess
Title: Rust-Based LOWESS Smoothing
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Amir", "Valizadeh", email = "thisisamirv@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides high-performance LOWESS smoothing (Locally Weighted Scatterplot Smoothing) 
    using a Rust backend. Supports various weight functions, robustness iterations, 
    streaming/online processing, and cross-validation.
License: AGPL-3 + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc (only required when installing from source)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
